@DayFlowAPI_HostAddress = https://localhost:7103
@token = token

### Login
POST {{DayFlowAPI_HostAddress}}/api/Auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "email@provider.com",
  "password": "passsword"
}

### Get ToDo
GET {{DayFlowAPI_HostAddress}}/api/ToDo
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}